data.description:
Welcome to paradise in the desert. Sitting on 1.28 acres this home is surrounded by breathtaking lush landscape including 54 fruit trees! The outdoors also offers a fenced-in garden, shade house, chicken coop, and a fire pit. An irrigation system is in place to water the garden. Our Attached garage is fully finished, has 2 windows, a mini-split installed, and can be easily converted to additional living space adding approximately 400 sqft.
Plenty of Storage and workshop space! This property comes with a 9ft by 9ft metal shed, an 8ft by 8ft barn, and a detachable metal garage 24ft wide by 35ft long by 15.5ft high. The detached garage is built by Absolute Steel, and offers a 12ft by 12ft roll-up door, pedestrian door, and 2 windows insulated, with electricity 110/220.
The inside of this home offers vaulted ceilings and an open-concept floor plan, great for entertaining. Additional updates to the home include all new paint, new kitchen cabinets, sink, new faucets, and new granite countertops. New shower heads and faucets in both bathrooms. New beautiful floor tile. 5 new windows (south side of the house) by Andersen Renewal.
Items that will stay with the property.
Foyer furniture, shelves in kids' rooms, AC split unit in the garage, Cedarwood playground, safe, and workshop.
This home is a must-see!
